title: Cheesy Mexican Kidney Bean & Veggie Nachos with Charred Corn Salsa & Pickled Onions
description: We turned the best things about nachos (the beans) into something irresistible and it’s all thanks to our Mexican Fiesta spice blend. We’ve also added fresh corn salsa and a dollop of plant-based mayo so you can enjoy an explosion of flavour with every bite.
